WEBVTT

00:00.542 --> 00:01.835
Ah-hyuck!

00:02.877 --> 00:04.295
♪ H-h-h-hit it ♪

00:04.379 --> 00:06.047
♪ Like father, like son ♪

00:06.131 --> 00:08.591
♪ You're always number one ♪

00:08.675 --> 00:09.509
[both] Yes!

00:09.592 --> 00:11.344
♪ There's buddies There's pals ♪

00:11.428 --> 00:12.262
Yeah!

00:12.345 --> 00:14.431
♪ You always seem to work things out ♪

00:14.514 --> 00:16.641
♪ Can't you see you're two of a kind ♪

00:16.725 --> 00:18.810
♪ Lookin' for a real good time ♪

00:18.893 --> 00:19.978
Whoa!

00:20.311 --> 00:21.271
♪ A real good time ♪

00:21.354 --> 00:22.230
Aah!

00:22.355 --> 00:23.773
♪ Report to the Goof Troop ♪

00:23.857 --> 00:26.026
♪ And we'll always stick together ♪

00:26.109 --> 00:27.694
♪ Always stick together ♪

00:27.777 --> 00:29.362
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:29.446 --> 00:33.033
♪ The best of friends forever ♪

00:33.116 --> 00:35.076
♪ Side by side wherever we go ♪

00:35.160 --> 00:39.330
♪ We're always ready to roll ♪

00:39.414 --> 00:41.416
♪ Now, gimme a beat ♪

00:41.499 --> 00:42.625
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:42.709 --> 00:45.503
♪ And we always stick together ♪

00:45.587 --> 00:47.505
♪ Oh, we're the Goof Troop ♪

00:47.589 --> 00:51.384
♪ The best of friends forever ♪

00:51.468 --> 00:53.595
♪ Now we're callin' everyone ♪

00:53.678 --> 00:55.472
♪ Come along and join the fun ♪

00:55.555 --> 00:56.931
♪ Report to the Goof Troop ♪

00:57.015 --> 00:58.558
♪ Baa ba doo da bop baa ba doo bop ♪

00:58.641 --> 00:59.726
Yeah!

01:05.023 --> 01:07.359
[buzzing]

01:10.904 --> 01:12.655
[Goofy] More molasses, Peg.

01:12.739 --> 01:14.949
[Peg] Are you sure, Goofy?

01:15.033 --> 01:16.910
Yep. Another gallon or two.

01:20.622 --> 01:24.376
Shoofly pies need that
certain feety feelin'.

01:24.459 --> 01:26.711
Mm. Nope.

01:26.795 --> 01:27.921
Doesn't feel right yet.

01:28.004 --> 01:29.547
Last one in's a broken egg.

01:29.631 --> 01:31.091
Oh, no, you don't!

01:31.216 --> 01:32.884
But I wanna make pies, too.

01:32.967 --> 01:34.260
I'm a great scroosher.

01:34.386 --> 01:36.596
Sorry, dear, but Goofy's the kook--

01:36.680 --> 01:37.972
uh, cook today.

01:38.056 --> 01:39.641
We wouldn't be caught dead in his kitchen,

01:39.724 --> 01:41.851
except he needs a hand--foot--

01:42.143 --> 01:46.272
some help making his very
interesting shoofly pies.

01:46.356 --> 01:48.024
Creeper jeepers.

01:48.108 --> 01:49.734
My sentiments exactly.

01:54.239 --> 01:56.408
Shoo, fly. You don't get any.

02:11.464 --> 02:13.591
Wow, Mr. P.

02:13.675 --> 02:17.429
State-of-the-art,
top-of-the-line Hank 5000.

02:17.554 --> 02:20.140
With every hi-tech gadget money can buy.

02:20.223 --> 02:22.058
Here. Make yourself useful,

02:22.142 --> 02:25.311
and I might let you look
at it through the window.

02:25.395 --> 02:28.148
Think of the games we
can play with this, Max.

02:28.231 --> 02:29.399
Right on, dude.

02:29.482 --> 02:32.736
Boxing gorillas, 50 flies from Fiji,

02:32.819 --> 02:35.030
and UFO masters.

02:36.448 --> 02:38.074
[buzz]

02:40.118 --> 02:43.329
We got a paragraph 7, subsection "D".

02:43.496 --> 02:45.540
Oh, OK. Here we go.

02:45.623 --> 02:47.751
[mumbles]

02:47.834 --> 02:48.960
[buzz]

02:49.044 --> 02:52.005
Put cable "a" into slot "b"--

02:52.088 --> 02:54.341
Outta my face, ya bug!

02:54.424 --> 02:57.969
You're about to make
your mark in literature.

02:58.053 --> 02:59.220
Ha ha ha!

03:03.266 --> 03:05.393
-[raspberry]
-You no-good flyin',

03:05.477 --> 03:08.271
six-legged, interruptin'
little pest anyway.

03:11.316 --> 03:13.234
Hey! What do you think you're doin'?

03:13.318 --> 03:15.612
Uh, helping you, sir.

03:15.737 --> 03:17.155
You spuds hit the road.

03:17.238 --> 03:20.450
Don't even breathe
in the same room with my Hank 5000.

03:23.370 --> 03:24.954
Huh! Kids.

03:25.038 --> 03:26.998
Good thing you can write
'em off at tax time.

03:27.082 --> 03:29.584
Otherwise they wouldn't
be any good at all.

03:29.668 --> 03:32.045
[buzz]

03:32.128 --> 03:33.713
You again?

03:33.797 --> 03:35.799
Will you get away!
Coime here, you little--

03:35.882 --> 03:37.759
I gotcha!

03:37.842 --> 03:40.345
You're askin' for it, bugsy.

03:43.348 --> 03:44.849
Coast is clear.

03:44.933 --> 03:46.559
Games away, dude!

03:46.643 --> 03:50.438
Now, let's see, it...
Uh...Oh, boy.

03:50.522 --> 03:52.857
This is more complicated
than I thought, Max.

03:52.941 --> 03:55.819
Ah, gimme a break, Peej.

03:55.902 --> 03:57.779
Don't we need the instructions?

03:57.862 --> 03:59.781
Instructions are for adults.

03:59.864 --> 04:01.533
Get with the program, dude.

04:10.583 --> 04:12.168
[Max] Look out!

04:12.252 --> 04:15.046
Musta crossed some cables or something.

04:15.130 --> 04:19.092
You bust Hank,
and my dad'll cross my cables for good!

04:19.175 --> 04:21.136
You worry too much.

04:21.219 --> 04:23.054
Only since we became friends.

04:23.138 --> 04:24.347
[doorbell rings]

04:27.100 --> 04:28.977
Here ya go, Peg.

04:29.060 --> 04:30.270
These are for you and Petey boy.

04:30.353 --> 04:33.273
Oh, well, thank you, Goofy,

04:33.356 --> 04:36.026
but it's really not necessary.

04:36.109 --> 04:39.529
Think nothing of it.
Where would you like 'em?

04:39.612 --> 04:40.822
Tacoma.

04:40.905 --> 04:42.365
I mean, put 'em anywhere, I guess.

04:42.449 --> 04:44.909
Just not on the kitchen table!

04:46.077 --> 04:48.246
One of the legs is loose.

04:48.329 --> 04:50.832
Ah-hyuck! Don't worry, Peg.
Got plenty more.

04:50.915 --> 04:54.210
Don't bother, Goofy. Please...

04:54.294 --> 04:55.462
Don't bother.

04:55.545 --> 04:57.922
Shucks, it ain't no bother at all.

05:00.091 --> 05:01.551
Read it and weep.

05:01.634 --> 05:03.428
60 trillion, dude.

05:03.511 --> 05:05.347
Beat that, sucker.

05:05.472 --> 05:08.308
Ha! With both eyes tied behind my back,

05:08.391 --> 05:09.768
Max-a-mundo.

05:09.934 --> 05:11.394
[Pete muttering]

05:11.478 --> 05:13.646
Old Hank'll tell me how
to murderlate flies.

05:13.730 --> 05:16.024
-My dad!
-We're dead!

05:23.365 --> 05:24.699
Hey...

05:24.783 --> 05:28.328
Somebody's been messin'
with my Hank 5000.

05:28.411 --> 05:32.499
When I find those spuds,
I'll peel them, too!

05:36.127 --> 05:37.629
A game!

05:38.046 --> 05:40.465
Those kids were playin' a game

05:40.548 --> 05:42.634
on my business computer!

05:42.717 --> 05:43.968
[buzz]

05:44.052 --> 05:46.388
You? Why, I'll...

05:46.471 --> 05:49.099
I'll...I'll teach you to bug me!

05:49.182 --> 05:51.142
Gotcha! Ha ha ha!

05:51.226 --> 05:52.435
Whoaaa!

05:55.980 --> 05:57.524
Hey, look, Max.

05:57.607 --> 05:59.567
50 flies from Fiji.

05:59.651 --> 06:02.028
Sit back and watch a champ, chump.

06:12.997 --> 06:15.083
Awesome! 49 to go.

06:15.250 --> 06:16.251
Hey, what's goin' on here?

06:17.627 --> 06:21.881
Say, I feel kinda weird.

06:22.007 --> 06:23.550
Oh. [screams]

06:23.633 --> 06:25.051
Almost got him!

06:25.135 --> 06:27.721
He's quick, man.
Must be the head ninja fly.

06:27.804 --> 06:30.473
He's worth 1,000 points, and he's mine.

06:30.640 --> 06:34.352
No! Hey!

06:34.477 --> 06:36.438
Whoa! Aah!

06:36.521 --> 06:38.356
I won! I won!

06:38.440 --> 06:41.192
Peeeeejaaaaay!

06:41.276 --> 06:42.152
It's your pop.

06:42.235 --> 06:43.236
Bye.

06:52.203 --> 06:54.622
Whoa. Oh, I, uh...

06:54.706 --> 06:56.916
I musta been dreamin'.

06:57.000 --> 06:58.376
Yeah, I was dreamin'.

07:00.211 --> 07:01.338
Hey.

07:01.421 --> 07:03.757
I'm hairy and legged.

07:03.840 --> 07:05.425
I--I got wings.

07:05.508 --> 07:06.885
I must be dreamin'.

07:06.968 --> 07:09.387
That's it. Just gotta pinch myself.

07:09.679 --> 07:12.140
Yeow! I'm never gonna do that again.

07:12.223 --> 07:13.308
Why...

07:14.476 --> 07:16.811
I'm a... I'm a fly?

07:16.895 --> 07:18.438
[P.J.] He's gone.

07:18.521 --> 07:21.399
Great. Let's get some more game time
before your dad gets back.

07:21.483 --> 07:23.777
My turn, dude. Stand back.

07:23.860 --> 07:26.696
Hey. It's not 50 flies from Fiji.

07:26.780 --> 07:28.323
It's boxing gorillas.

07:28.406 --> 07:30.241
Cool! P.J.! Son! Don't touch Hank!

07:30.325 --> 07:32.077
It's my only way back to bein' me!

07:32.160 --> 07:33.244
Aah!

07:35.538 --> 07:40.669
Uh, maybe we shouldn't mess
with my dad's computer anymore.

07:40.752 --> 07:42.796
I'm feelin' real guilty,

07:42.879 --> 07:45.131
like he's kind of,
I don't know, watchin' me?

07:45.215 --> 07:46.591
I gotta get their attention.

07:46.675 --> 07:49.177
Ha ha! Boy, has he got you trained.

07:50.762 --> 07:53.139
Yeow! That fly bit me!

07:56.351 --> 07:59.688
Hey, uncup me, you flynappin' spud!
Hey! Hey!

08:14.285 --> 08:15.120
Ohh.

08:15.286 --> 08:17.205
The Goof! He'll help me.

08:23.378 --> 08:24.713
Mmm.

08:24.796 --> 08:26.423
Shoofly pie.

08:26.506 --> 08:28.633
Mm, what a tasty smell.

08:28.717 --> 08:30.176
Huh?

08:30.260 --> 08:33.513
A fly in my shoofly pie. A-hyuck.

08:33.680 --> 08:36.224
Ya shoofly pie fly-paperin' Goof.

08:36.307 --> 08:37.851
I'm gonna--hey!

08:37.934 --> 08:40.395
Aw. Poor little feller. Here.

08:40.478 --> 08:41.771
Let me clean ya up.

08:42.856 --> 08:43.732
I don't wanna--

08:43.815 --> 08:46.067
[sputtering]

08:46.151 --> 08:48.528
Aah! Aah! Aah!

08:48.611 --> 08:50.613
Whoa! Haah!

08:50.697 --> 08:52.240
There ya go.

08:56.244 --> 08:59.622
Shoulda known better
than trust a Goof to give a fly a hand.

09:06.004 --> 09:08.214
What am I gonna do?

09:08.298 --> 09:10.300
[Peg] Pete, I don't know where you are,

09:10.383 --> 09:11.843
but I know you can hear me.

09:11.926 --> 09:13.261
Chop that tree down,

09:13.345 --> 09:15.305
or you're gonna sleep under it tonight!

09:15.347 --> 09:18.266
Popsicle lips. She'll help me.

09:26.024 --> 09:27.567
Peg o' my heart!

09:27.650 --> 09:28.943
Sweetie!

09:29.027 --> 09:30.904
It's your hammock honey bear.

09:30.987 --> 09:33.573
Your buzzin' Petey fly.

09:33.656 --> 09:36.201
Pegums can't hear me.

09:36.284 --> 09:37.869
I gotta get closer.

09:38.870 --> 09:40.163
Peg!

09:40.246 --> 09:42.624
Peg, it's me--Pete!

09:42.832 --> 09:45.669
Daddy's home, sweetie-pie.

09:45.752 --> 09:47.754
Pete, where are you?

09:47.837 --> 09:48.755
Right here!

09:48.838 --> 09:49.839
Where's here?

09:49.923 --> 09:51.675
Right...here!

09:51.758 --> 09:53.426
No. No, no.

09:53.510 --> 09:55.762
No, no, aah!

09:55.845 --> 09:57.847
Eeeeeeee...

10:00.225 --> 10:01.768
Ticket!

10:05.397 --> 10:06.523
Uh-oh.

10:06.606 --> 10:09.150
This ain't no trampoline.

10:09.234 --> 10:12.278
I hope we're havin' an earthquake.

10:13.613 --> 10:15.448
Oh, mama!

10:18.118 --> 10:19.703
Nice spider.

10:19.786 --> 10:24.124
Nice, ugly, droolin',
hairy, hungry spider.

10:24.207 --> 10:27.711
Help me!

10:33.091 --> 10:34.759
Get me outta this one.

10:34.843 --> 10:36.553
And I'll be good. I'll be really good.

10:36.636 --> 10:38.179
No more cheating my consumers.

10:38.263 --> 10:39.889
No more-- [buzzing]

10:48.273 --> 10:50.108
No! Hey, watch it!

10:55.363 --> 10:56.865
Look at all the bugs.

10:56.948 --> 10:59.534
I gotta get a bigger bug light.

11:05.123 --> 11:09.085
Ouch! I can't get used to these hands.

11:10.670 --> 11:11.880
New recruit?

11:11.963 --> 11:13.631
Yes, sir.

11:20.847 --> 11:24.476
Shanghaied in my own sycamore.

11:26.686 --> 11:28.313
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:28.396 --> 11:30.023
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:30.106 --> 11:32.025
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:32.108 --> 11:33.610
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:33.693 --> 11:35.195
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:35.278 --> 11:36.613
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:36.696 --> 11:38.365
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:38.448 --> 11:42.994
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:43.203 --> 11:46.915
I'll hut you, ya lousy--

11:46.998 --> 11:47.832
[gulp]

11:47.916 --> 11:50.377
[buzzing]

11:50.460 --> 11:52.545
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

11:52.629 --> 11:53.672
Yeah.

11:59.969 --> 12:01.137
Hey!

12:01.221 --> 12:02.931
Whoa!

12:07.143 --> 12:09.396
Heh heh. Me?

12:10.855 --> 12:12.774
Have you boys seen Pete?

12:12.857 --> 12:14.609
No, Mrs. P.

12:14.693 --> 12:16.778
Haven't seen him
since he went after the fly, Mom.

12:17.487 --> 12:19.322
Have you seen Daddy, dear?

12:19.406 --> 12:21.116
Uh-huh. Lotsa times.

12:21.199 --> 12:22.701
No, sweetheart.

12:22.784 --> 12:24.911
I meant have you seen Daddy lately?

12:25.036 --> 12:26.788
Maybe he's playing hide-and-seek.

12:26.913 --> 12:27.914
I'll find him!

12:28.039 --> 12:30.792
Ohh, an island vacation,

12:30.875 --> 12:33.086
no one around for miles.

12:38.508 --> 12:41.052
What are we, men or flies?

12:41.136 --> 12:42.595
Flies!

12:42.679 --> 12:45.640
Lousy, stinkin' flies.

12:45.724 --> 12:47.767
Here is our target.

12:48.977 --> 12:49.853
My house?

12:49.936 --> 12:52.689
We're invadin' my house?

12:52.772 --> 12:55.108
Here is our enemy.

12:56.234 --> 12:59.487
We'll see about that, ya maggot.

12:59.571 --> 13:01.364
No fly-by-night flies

13:01.448 --> 13:03.950
is gonna track my house up with fly feet.

13:11.499 --> 13:14.711
Huh. This'll bungle those bugs.

13:14.794 --> 13:16.379
Ha ha!

13:19.966 --> 13:21.384
Hut, 2, 3, 4.

13:21.468 --> 13:25.221
Hut, 2, 3, 4...

13:25.764 --> 13:28.058
[plays charge]

13:28.475 --> 13:30.810
[blows whistle]

13:37.650 --> 13:38.818
Aim!

13:43.073 --> 13:45.241
No!

13:48.703 --> 13:52.540
That major maggot's a general nuisance!

13:53.291 --> 13:54.542
What are you doing?

13:54.668 --> 13:57.045
Making Mommy nice for Daddy.

13:57.128 --> 13:58.755
There's an old expression--

13:58.838 --> 14:01.591
you get more flies with honey.

14:01.675 --> 14:02.884
Ha ha ha.

14:02.967 --> 14:04.469
Help me, love butter.

14:04.552 --> 14:06.638
Come on, Peg, help me.

14:06.721 --> 14:08.098
It's me!

14:08.181 --> 14:10.266
I'll look nice for Daddy, too.

14:10.350 --> 14:14.270
Aw, isn't that cute?

14:14.354 --> 14:17.065
He'll love that, dear.

14:17.148 --> 14:18.024
[sputtering]

14:18.108 --> 14:20.235
[coughing]

14:20.318 --> 14:21.569
Uh-oh.

14:23.363 --> 14:26.074
Look, you caught a fly already.

14:26.157 --> 14:28.910
Get that fly out of my ointment, dear.

14:29.035 --> 14:32.497
Poor little fly. He needs a bath.

14:32.580 --> 14:33.832
Sure, go ahead.

14:33.915 --> 14:37.252
Drown Daddy,
ya little...

14:38.044 --> 14:39.462
Help! Help!

14:39.546 --> 14:40.964
Ah-choo!

14:41.047 --> 14:43.008
The flies are comin', ya dipsticks.

14:43.091 --> 14:44.801
Ah-choo!

14:44.884 --> 14:47.387
No, no! Yeee!

14:49.514 --> 14:51.433
Hey! Hey, you spuds!

14:51.516 --> 14:53.309
The flies are comin'!

14:53.393 --> 14:54.894
The flies are--

14:54.978 --> 14:56.271
Not now! I'm trying to--

14:56.354 --> 14:58.148
Uh-oh.

15:05.572 --> 15:07.741
[clears throat]

15:09.034 --> 15:10.243
Traitor.

15:11.953 --> 15:13.246
[kicccct]

15:15.248 --> 15:19.044
Does [kicccct] mean what I think it means,

15:19.127 --> 15:21.004
ya winged nut?

15:21.087 --> 15:22.756
[gulp]

15:29.137 --> 15:31.056
Goofy, have you seen Pete?

15:31.181 --> 15:33.725
Sure, Peg. Lotsa times.

15:33.808 --> 15:35.268
Hyuck.

15:35.352 --> 15:36.978
No, Goofy.

15:37.062 --> 15:38.313
I mean lately.

15:38.396 --> 15:41.274
Hmm. Uh, nope. Not lately.

15:41.358 --> 15:42.984
I hate to ask you, Goofy,

15:43.068 --> 15:45.528
but would you chop down the sycamore?

15:45.612 --> 15:47.655
Pete's never gonna get around to it.

15:47.739 --> 15:49.824
Be glad to, Peg.

16:06.966 --> 16:08.927
Hey, no blindfold. I'll tell you what.

16:09.010 --> 16:11.513
I'll wear one if you do, too.
That'll even the odds.

16:11.596 --> 16:13.473
Whatta ya say, huh? Hey!

16:13.556 --> 16:14.599
Ready...

16:15.934 --> 16:17.769
Nope. I'm not ready.

16:18.645 --> 16:19.729
Aim...

16:19.813 --> 16:22.315
How'd you like a car?

16:22.399 --> 16:23.525
Big car with a--

16:25.235 --> 16:26.986
ha! They missed.

16:27.070 --> 16:28.321
Charge!

16:28.405 --> 16:30.657
Anybody out there? Yoo-hoo.

16:33.785 --> 16:36.371
Hey! Get away! Shoo, flies.

16:36.454 --> 16:38.289
I got a tree to timber.

16:39.082 --> 16:40.166
Hey!

16:40.250 --> 16:41.793
Don't get personal.

16:41.876 --> 16:42.752
Hyuck!

16:42.836 --> 16:43.920
Ow! Ow!

16:44.004 --> 16:45.046
Whoa!

16:53.638 --> 16:56.141
[fly talk]

16:59.436 --> 17:01.146
[kissing]

17:04.941 --> 17:07.777
Help me out, you spuds!

17:07.902 --> 17:09.070
[buzz]

17:09.154 --> 17:11.656
Ooh, it's the mean fly, Peej.

17:11.740 --> 17:13.241
Hold still. I'll get it.

17:13.324 --> 17:14.367
Aah!

17:17.454 --> 17:19.831
I just hope those two
pudding heads can read.

17:23.293 --> 17:25.587
Don't...move...fly.

17:25.670 --> 17:27.380
Wait Peej. What?

17:27.505 --> 17:29.841
That fly spelled "help" on your face.

17:29.924 --> 17:31.676
He spelled it backwards.

17:33.470 --> 17:34.721
[laughing]

17:34.804 --> 17:36.222
H--h--hey!

17:36.306 --> 17:37.766
Cut it out!

17:37.849 --> 17:40.977
Why is Max's daddy dancin' in our yard?

17:41.061 --> 17:43.646
I have no idea, Pistol.

17:43.730 --> 17:45.148
Lock the door.

17:45.231 --> 17:46.483
Mom,

17:46.566 --> 17:49.361
you're not gonna believe this.

17:51.529 --> 17:53.448
Daddy, Daddy, Daddy?

17:53.531 --> 17:55.617
Disgusto-mundo.

17:55.700 --> 17:57.827
I just can't believe

17:57.911 --> 18:00.830
this gross, disgusting little thing

18:00.914 --> 18:02.207
is my husband!

18:02.290 --> 18:04.042
What's the big surprise?

18:04.125 --> 18:05.293
What's he saying, Mommy?

18:05.377 --> 18:06.961
The flies are comin'!

18:07.045 --> 18:09.172
The flies are comin'!

18:09.255 --> 18:13.760
Your father-- if I can read
his fly-sized lips--

18:13.843 --> 18:16.638
says...the flies are coming.

18:16.721 --> 18:18.098
Attack!

18:18.181 --> 18:21.142
♪ We are flies, and we are mean ♪

18:21.226 --> 18:22.977
♪ Meanest flies you've ever seen ♪

18:23.061 --> 18:25.146
-♪ Sound off ♪
-♪ 1, 2 ♪

18:25.230 --> 18:27.148
-♪ Sound off ♪
-♪ 3, 4 ♪

18:27.232 --> 18:29.109
-♪ Sound off ♪
-♪ 1, 2 ♪

18:29.192 --> 18:30.985
-♪ Sound off ♪
-♪ 3, 4 ♪

18:31.069 --> 18:32.445
I hate that song.

18:32.529 --> 18:35.115
I hate that song,
and they're comin' to get me!

18:35.198 --> 18:37.325
They're comin' to get
me with the [kicccct].

18:37.409 --> 18:39.661
Help me, help me!

18:40.537 --> 18:42.205
Mr P is right!

18:42.330 --> 18:44.416
[P.J.] The flies are comin'!

18:50.505 --> 18:51.464
Yeah!

18:51.548 --> 18:52.841
I got the suckers!

18:52.924 --> 18:53.883
[doorbell rings]

18:54.968 --> 18:56.052
Who is it?

18:56.136 --> 18:57.512
[flies] Telegram.

18:57.595 --> 18:58.972
Telegram?

19:03.393 --> 19:05.311
Ah-hyuck! Say there, stranger.

19:05.395 --> 19:07.564
You seen any flies around here?

19:07.647 --> 19:08.606
[buzzing]

19:08.690 --> 19:10.900
If you do, watch out,

19:10.984 --> 19:14.195
'cause they're frisky little fellers.

19:14.863 --> 19:16.031
Gawrsh!

19:16.114 --> 19:17.949
Aah! Ooh-hoo-hoo!

19:18.033 --> 19:20.660
It's a trick. Bring the buckets, boys!

19:21.411 --> 19:23.538
Set? Let 'em have it!

19:26.416 --> 19:27.709
Thanks for the bath,

19:27.792 --> 19:29.836
but we got flies to the eyes out here.

19:36.426 --> 19:38.136
This is the end!

19:38.303 --> 19:39.429
Aah!

19:40.221 --> 19:41.931
-Aah!
-Aah!

19:42.015 --> 19:44.059
What are we gonna do, Max?

19:44.142 --> 19:46.311
This screamin' isn't helpin' me think.

19:46.394 --> 19:48.688
Oopsie. Did I scream?

19:49.856 --> 19:51.191
Ice cream! Ice cream!

19:51.274 --> 19:53.276
This is no time for ice cream.

19:53.360 --> 19:56.946
But it is time for a 64-flavor diversion.

19:57.364 --> 19:59.074
[bell rings]

20:02.494 --> 20:04.996
I knew these pies'd be good for somethin'.

20:05.080 --> 20:06.414
Mmm.

20:06.498 --> 20:07.582
Yummy!

20:07.665 --> 20:09.417
Attack!

20:17.425 --> 20:18.343
[P.J.] Here they come!

20:20.136 --> 20:21.346
Hurry!

20:23.723 --> 20:25.767
That'll cool off their feedin' frenzy.

20:25.850 --> 20:27.018
Hyuck!

20:28.019 --> 20:29.938
[slurping]

20:32.941 --> 20:34.401
[burp]

20:35.860 --> 20:38.321
Your pop musta done
somethin' to the computer

20:38.405 --> 20:40.031
to make himself a fly.

20:40.115 --> 20:42.826
Yeah, right, so all we have to do

20:42.909 --> 20:45.662
is what he did only backwards?

20:45.745 --> 20:49.416
Works for me.
I do it all the time. Hyuck! Ha ha ha ha!

20:49.708 --> 20:52.168
A quiet island, no kids,

20:52.252 --> 20:54.421
no bug husband to bug me,

20:54.504 --> 20:57.424
just sand, sun, and surf.

20:58.091 --> 20:59.634
And silence!

20:59.718 --> 21:01.344
[Max] Smile, Mr. P.

21:02.012 --> 21:04.347
I'll give ya a smile, ya--

21:04.431 --> 21:06.057
gaaah!

21:08.685 --> 21:10.311
Ooohh!

21:10.395 --> 21:12.939
Goody, goody, goody,
goody, goody, goody!

21:15.567 --> 21:17.318
-Uh, hit another button.
-Right, dude!

21:17.402 --> 21:19.821
Whoa! Oh! Oh! Moo!

21:19.904 --> 21:22.157
Gotta hit "P" for Pete.

21:25.577 --> 21:29.789
Oh, you Goof, stay away from my computer!

21:30.999 --> 21:32.876
[Goofy] Just look what you did, Pete.

21:34.586 --> 21:36.129
[raspberry]

21:38.923 --> 21:41.760
Hank, you're outta here!

21:43.219 --> 21:45.263
[buzzing]

21:46.765 --> 21:48.391
[knock on door]

21:50.769 --> 21:53.355
Isn't that somebody at the door, P.J.?

21:53.438 --> 21:54.814
It's for you, Dad.

21:54.939 --> 21:57.025
I have to do everything around here.

21:57.108 --> 21:58.902
You'd think a fly--guy--

21:58.985 --> 22:01.488
could get some peace
and quiet for a change.

22:01.571 --> 22:03.948
Am I right?
You bet I am, boy.

22:04.783 --> 22:07.285
Oooooohhh.

22:07.369 --> 22:08.953
This can't be happening.

22:09.037 --> 22:11.289
This is all a bad dream.

22:11.373 --> 22:13.041
[kicccct]

22:13.124 --> 22:14.542
Oh, mama!

22:18.463 --> 22:19.547
♪ Gimme a beat ♪

22:19.631 --> 22:21.716
[theme music playing]

22:46.408 --> 22:47.617
Yeah.
